<a href="http://www.tralac.org/cgi-bin/giga.cgi?cmd=cause_dir_news_item&amp;news_id=42867&amp;cause_id=1694" target="_self">http://www.tralac.org/cgi-bin/giga.cgi?cmd=cause_dir_news_item&amp;news_...</a></p><p>3. TRALAC, point of access to SADC–EAC–COMESA Tripartite Free-Trade Area legal texts (drafts), January 2011</p><p>
<a href="http://www.tralac.org/cgi-bin/giga.cgi?cmd=cause_dir_news_item&amp;cause_id=1694&amp;news_id=97849&amp;cat_id=1036" target="_self">http://www.tralac.org/cgi-bin/giga.cgi?cmd=cause_dir_news_item&amp;cause...</a></p><p>4. TRALAC/Konrad-Adenauer-Stiftung, ‘Monitoring regional integration in Southern Africa: yearbook 2010’, 2011</p><p>
